    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/6ad60e9c114fbe22f0e1130f565f8c65.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/6ad60e9c114fbe22f0e1130f565f8c65.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/6ad60e9c114fbe22f0e1130f565f8c65.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>屡获殊荣的《奇异人生》开始了一个大胆的新时代，扮演全新的主角，解开惊心动魄的谜团！<br><br>本作主角——艾黎克丝·陈长期以来一直压抑着自己背负的“诅咒”：她拥有能感知、吸收甚至是操纵他人强烈情绪的能力。这些情绪会以炽烈的彩色光环呈现在她眼前。<br><br>当她的哥哥在一次所谓的事故中不幸去世时，艾黎克丝不得不使用她那不稳定的超能力来寻找真相——并揭开小镇之下所埋藏的黑暗秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >令人难以接受的真相</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/c073ec8f42fbafde0a6193c98f7b70e9.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/c073ec8f42fbafde0a6193c98f7b70e9.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/c073ec8f42fbafde0a6193c98f7b70e9.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在一场充斥着跌宕起伏情感的冒险之中，挖掘哥哥死亡背后的惊人秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受一切</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/1ba051b23d3fb7e24b2ae59c7ba07cb4.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/1ba051b23d3fb7e24b2ae59c7ba07cb4.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/1ba051b23d3fb7e24b2ae59c7ba07cb4.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>用“共情感应”的力量改变命运与人生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难以割舍的羁绊</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b7c07fb846094de33d1d45e5b7155d0d.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b7c07fb846094de33d1d45e5b7155d0d.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b7c07fb846094de33d1d45e5b7155d0d.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与小镇居民建立信任——并与瑞恩和斯蒂芬发展友谊或浪漫爱情。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >讲述真情实感的故事</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/4e9ba9219fe958f5aa24d7c773a257ee.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/4e9ba9219fe958f5aa24d7c773a257ee.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/4e9ba9219fe958f5aa24d7c773a257ee.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>做出艰难的决定，选择自己的未来。自由漫步在港泉镇的街道、商店以及鲜有人至的角落，邂逅令人难以忘怀忘的角色。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >表达你自己</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/cd47f85fbb2fb84f08f55e1ccd041376.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/cd47f85fbb2fb84f08f55e1ccd041376.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/cd47f85fbb2fb84f08f55e1ccd041376.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>决定艾黎克丝的穿着打扮，多达 24 套时装可供选择。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独家音轨</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b456197c5de106dd17c8c0953b34ca80.poster.avif?t=1771867255\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b456197c5de106dd17c8c0953b34ca80.webm?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936790/extras/b456197c5de106dd17c8c0953b34ca80.mp4?t=1771867255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Girl in Red、Alt-J、Portugal, The Man、Hayley Kiyoko、Maribou State等音乐家的热门曲目会伴随斯蒂芬的旅程。",
